<template>
  <dashboard-modal 
  :uppy="uppy" 
  :open="open" 
  :props="{
    onRequestCloseModal: handleClose
  }"/>
</template>

<script>
import Uppy from '@uppy/core'
import { DashboardModal } from '@uppy/vue'

export default {
  components: {
    DashboardModal
  },
  computed: {
    uppy: () => new Uppy()
  },
  data () {
    return {
      open: false
    }
  },
  methods: {
    handleClose() { this.open = false }
  }
}
</script>
